author: Maria Armental
title: Carl Icahn’s New Website ‘Coming Soon’
text:
Billionaire investor Carl Icahn is launching another website to make his views known.
The new site—CarlIcahn.com, now a landing page that Is expected to be updated Thursday evening—adds to a series of websites and social media accounts on which Mr. Icahn periodically posts commentaries and announcements that fall under public disclosure rules of the Securities and Exchange Commission.
